attention to you very often.

17:52.870 --> 17:54.800
-That's about right.
-Sinjin, my boy, I love ya,

17:54.800 --> 17:56.370
but the world don't
revolve around you.

17:56.370 --> 17:57.800
It revolves around me.

17:57.810 --> 18:00.110
-You ready?
-Yeah.

18:00.110 --> 18:01.610
Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa! Whoa!

