-What?
-Got a prize for you guys.

18:03.610 --> 18:05.550
You probably didn't even
know this, but I have a stepson.

18:05.550 --> 18:09.020
What? What the [bleep]?
I mean, where do I even start?

18:09.020 --> 18:10.420
A stepson?
-[ chuckles ]

18:10.420 --> 18:11.880
I've been here for,
like, five years,

18:11.890 --> 18:13.420
and this is the first
I've ever heard

18:13.420 --> 18:14.950
of richard rawlings
having a stepson.

18:14.960 --> 18:17.960
He's gonna handle some
social media stuff, so...

18:17.960 --> 18:19.660
Okay, so is he gonna
follow us or what?

18:19.660 --> 18:22.330
-Nope. He's gonna ride with ya.
-In<i> this</i> van?

18:22.330 --> 18:23.530
Richard: Yep. Get in there.

18:23.530 --> 18:25.130
But there's not even
a seat for me!

18:25.130 --> 18:26.370
Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa.

18:26.370 --> 18:27.600
You got your camera
and your cellphone, right?

18:27.600 --> 18:28.770
-Yeah.
-All right, go.

18:28.770 --> 18:31.570
-Why is he going with us?
-Get on in.

18:31.570 --> 18:32.740
Trial by fire.
-That's not even...

18:32.740 --> 18:33.940
Sleep with your back
to the wall,

18:33.940 --> 18:35.780
