trouble, don't call me.

18:35.780 --> 18:37.640
-What's that smell in here?
-Y'all good to go.

18:37.650 --> 18:38.980
His name's sinjin.
-Sinjin?

18:38.980 --> 18:40.950
Yeah, don't worry
about the definition.

18:40.950 --> 18:42.120
I don't
understand it either.

18:42.120 --> 18:43.380
-Is he indian?
-I don't know.

18:43.380 --> 18:44.650
-Does he have money?
-Nope.

18:44.650 --> 18:45.850
Why's he gotta go
with us though?

18:45.850 --> 18:48.590
900 miles without a/c,
that's already bad enough,

18:48.590 --> 18:50.190
and now we got
little richard?

18:50.190 --> 18:51.860
[ scoffs ] whatever.

18:54.900 --> 18:57.000
-Mike: Sinjin, huh?
-Yeah.

18:57.000 --> 18:58.700
-Well, I'm mike.
-Okay.

18:58.700 --> 19:00.730
And snitches get
stitches in this van.

