19:05.670 --> 19:08.940
No.
I was supposed to do my job.

19:08.940 --> 19:10.140
Mike:
There goes our plans.

19:11.710 --> 19:13.110
Richard: All right, man,
get social media.

19:13.110 --> 19:15.480
Click, bing, take pictures,
have fun.

19:15.480 --> 19:17.350
If he doesn't do good,
leave him there.

19:17.350 --> 19:18.520
-Mike: Oh, we will.
-Oh, we'll leave him there,

19:18.520 --> 19:20.850
that's for sure.

19:20.860 --> 19:23.420
His mom said, "give him a job."
I gave him a job.

19:23.420 --> 19:26.690
That's your introduction to
my stepson, sinjin venegas.

19:26.690 --> 19:28.490
Now I married his mom
when he was 3.

19:28.500 --> 19:30.600
He just graduated
